(Marimba CNC Bar And Resonator Build Packet - page 3 of 20) Tj T*
( ) Tj T*
() Tj T*
( Arch Undercut) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The workbook defines a linear MIDI-scaled arch-depth schedule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    arch_depth = \(edge_thickness - min_center_thickness\)  min\(1, \(96 - midi\)/48\)) Tj T*
(    center_thickness = edge_thickness - arch_depth) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This makes the low bars carry the deepest undercut and the high bars approach a shallow) Tj T*
(arch. The current minimum center thickness is 0.250 in, so C3 reaches the minimum while C6) Tj T*
(remains about 0.719 in at center.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The arch should be cut as a centered parabolic underside relief over roughly 60 percent of) Tj T*
(the bar length. Final voicing still requires controlled sanding and tuner checks; the) Tj T*
(workbook is the first-pass schedule.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
( Resonators) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The resonator tubes are treated as quarter-wave closed pipes:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    L_res = 13552 / \(4  f\) - 0.82  bore) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The sheet currently uses the bar-width column as the resonator bore/end-correction proxy.) Tj T*
(That is acceptable as a first-pass planning value, but the sourcing pass should decide real) Tj T*
(tube diameters and update family-spec.csv if the selected bore differs from the workbook) Tj T*
(proxy.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The distinction is important:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Bar pitch is tuned by bar length, thickness, arch geometry, and material.) Tj T*
(- Resonator length is tuned to reinforce the already-tuned bar frequency.) Tj T*
(- A resonator mismatch changes sustain/loudness/color; it does not fix a wrong bar pitch.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
( Bar Schedule) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The full schedule is in family-spec.csv. Representative rows:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(| Note | MIDI | Target Hz | Length in | Width in | Node 1 in | Node 2 in | Arch in | Center) Tj T*
(in | Resonator in |) Tj T*
(| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |) Tj T*
(| C3 | 48 | 130.813 | 32.251 | 2.000 | 7.224 | 25.027 | 0.625 | 0.250 | 24.260 |) Tj T*
(| C4 | 60 | 261.626 | 22.805 | 1.750 | 5.108 | 17.697 | 0.469 | 0.406 | 11.515 |) Tj T*
(| A4 | 69 | 440.000 | 17.585 | 1.750 | 3.939 | 13.646 | 0.352 | 0.523 | 6.265 |) Tj T*
(| C6 | 84 | 1046.502 | 11.403 | 1.250 | 2.554 | 8.848 | 0.156 | 0.719 | 2.212 |) Tj T*
() Tj T*
( Resonator Schedule) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(family-spec.csv includes a first-pass tube length for every note. Treat these as cut-long) Tj T*
(values until a tube material, bore, cap style, and stopper/trim strategy are selected.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Recommended build behavior:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
ET
endstream
